If you ONLY want them to have your emergency info from your Medical ID, then deactivate Face ID/finger print to unlock. It is very easy for anyone to gain access to your iPhone with your face/finger when you are unable or unconscious. You never know when this can help someone!✨

Did not know this!
By setting up your Medical ID in your iPhone. (Go to Settings, Health, Medical ID) emergency services can access in two clicks the relevant info they need if you are in an emergency/accident or unconscious.(Your emergency contacts, allergies, medications, etc.) https://t.co/Q2PvRW2Q4U
